## 🔑 Key Features

### Authentication & Authorization
- JWT strategy với `@nestjs/passport`
- Token signing/verification với `@nestjs/jwt`
- Auth guards và decorators
- `@CurrentUser()` decorator để extract user từ JWT

### API Endpoints
- **REST API** cho web frontend (3-web)
  - Controllers trong `modules/{feature}/{feature}.controller.ts`
  - Routes: `/api/{resource}`
- **GraphQL API** cho mobile apps (5-mobile-ios, 6-mobile-android)
  - Resolvers trong `modules/{feature}/{feature}.resolver.ts`
  - Schema auto-generated từ resolvers
- **WebSocket** cho real-time communication
  - Socket.IO integration (via websocket-service)

### gRPC Clients
Gateway gọi các microservices thông qua gRPC:
- `users-client.ts` → users-service (port 3001) - ⭐ Gamification (F2P)
- `stories-client.ts` → stories-service (port 3002)
- `comments-client.ts` → comments-service (port 3003)
- `search-client.ts` → search-service (port 3004)
- `ai-client.ts` → ai-service (port 3005) - ⭐ Emotional AI Narration
- `notification-client.ts` → notification-service (port 3006)
- `websocket-client.ts` → websocket-service (port 3007)
- `social-client.ts` → social-service (port 3008)
- `community-client.ts` → community-service (port 3009) - ⭐ Paragraph Comments (Duanping)
- `monetization-client.ts` → monetization-service (port 3010) - ⭐ PPC & Privilege Models

### Modules Organization
Mỗi feature có một module riêng với:
- **Controller**: REST endpoints (cho web)
- **Resolver**: GraphQL resolvers (cho mobile)
- **Service**: Aggregates data from multiple gRPC calls (nếu cần)
- **Module**: NestJS module definition

### Caching Strategy
- **Gateway Cache (Redis)**: Caches frequently accessed data
  - Rankings: 1-hour TTL
  - Editor Picks: 30-min TTL
  - Genres: 24-hour TTL
  - Search results: 5-min TTL
  - Recommendations: 1-hour TTL

## ⚠️ Important Rules

**Rule #4:** Gateway is a "Bouncer", NOT the "Brain" - NO business logic!

Gateway chỉ có nhiệm vụ:
- ✅ **Authentication (AuthN)**: Validates JWT, extracts user info
- ✅ **Routing**: Directs traffic to correct internal service (via gRPC)
- ✅ **Rate Limiting**: Protects services from abuse (`@nestjs/throttler`)
- ✅ **Caching**: Caches responses to reduce load on services
- ✅ **WAF Integration**: Sits behind Cloudflare for security
- ❌ **KHÔNG có business logic**: All business logic in services

### Code Patterns

**REST Controller Example:**
```typescript
@Controller('api/stories')
export class StoriesController {
  @Get(':id')
  @UseGuards(JwtAuthGuard)
  async getStory(@Param('id') id: string, @CurrentUser() user: User) {
    // Call gRPC client, NO business logic
    return this.storiesClient.getStory({ id, userId: user.id });
  }
}
```

**GraphQL Resolver Example:**
```typescript
@Resolver(() => Story)
export class StoriesResolver {
  @Query(() => Story)
  @UseGuards(JwtAuthGuard)
  async story(@Args('id') id: string, @CurrentUser() user: User) {
    // Call gRPC client, NO business logic
    return this.storiesClient.getStory({ id, userId: user.id });
  }
}
```

